  <h2>Common Natural Wine Myths</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>❌ "All natural wines taste funky" - Many are clean and pure</li>
    <li>❌ "Natural wines don't age" - Great examples can age beautifully</li>
    <li>❌ "Natural wine is just a trend" - It's a return to historical methods</li>
    <li>❌ "Natural wines are always more expensive" - Many offer great value</li>
  </ul>

